	(text "Logic Pinouts\nPin 1: RPWM (Reverse Speed)\nPin 2: LPWM (Forward Speed)\nPin 3: R_EN (Reverse Enable)\nPin 4: L_EN (Forward Enable)\nPin 5: R_IS (Reverse Current Alarm - often left unconnected)\nPin 6: L_IS (Forward Current Alarm - often left unconnected)\nPin 7: VCC (5V Logic Power)\nPin 8: GND (Logic Ground)"
